Direct Known Subclasses:
ActivityEndEventContextImpl
public class EventContextImpl
extends LazyStoredEventContext
implements EventContext

A differed event. When an SBB posts an event, it winds up as one of these. When the tx commits, it actually makes it into the event queue.

Author:
M. Ranganathan, Ivelin Ivanov (refactoring), eduardomartins
